Cable Newspaper Journalism Foundation (CNJF), also known as the Cable Foundation, is seeking to recruit a highly motivated video editor to strengthen and expand its multimedia news and content production. Method of application: Interested persons should send their CVs, a work portfolio and a motivation letter of no more than 300 words to jobs@thecable.ng. The position applied for should be the subject of the e-mail. Women and persons living with disability are strongly encouraged to apply. Pay package: Competitive and negotiable Deadline: Friday, January 27.